parameters: It's good when a blonde delinquent interrupts a couple.
Did you have such a hobby?
That's why, President, please do it!

Damn Saru, in the end, you're saying I'm a blonde
delinquent, huh?

Uwaa, uwaaa! My neck is bending in the opposite direction!
It's going to break, it's really going to break!

While I briefly looked away, the president and Saruyama were
doing gymnastics in acrobatic poses that can only be
seen on YouTube.

Anyway, congratulations. Should I take care of the MC duties
later?
We won't break up! We can meet for thousands of years!
Well, there's no need to worry!
